#

Grilled Mackerel with Lemon and Herbs

20 min
$12
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

MediterraneanAmerican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickHealthyGrilled

Description

A simple and flavorful grilled mackerel dish, bursting with zesty lemon and fresh herbs.

Ingredients

  • mackerel fillets: 4
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon: 1, juiced
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
